data.description: Wonderful two story 3 beds on one level. Private 3/4 master bath. Main floor offers hardwood floors, a separate living room and family room to maximize all your space on the main level! Family room has its own fireplace with an entrance to the backyard that will give you so much natural light and fresh air. Kitchen has a large eat-in and a separate dining room also with entrance to the back yard. Lower level has a rec room, large laundry room with storage and a den. Add egress window for 4th bedroom. Windows, roof, electrical panel, driveway, furnace, water softener, refinished wood floors all under 8 years old. Do not miss out on this gem!
